Antwan Wiggins tí wọ́n bí ní ọjọ́ Kẹfà oṣù Kẹ́ta ọdún 1980 ( March 6, 1980) ní ìlú Brooklyn. jẹ́ ọ̀kọrin hip hop ọmọ orílẹ̀ èdè Amẹ́ríkà.[1] Orúkọ tí wọ́n mọ̀ọ́ pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ ni 'Awon'. 
Ní ọdún 2014, Ó dá ile- iṣẹ́ orin "Don't Sleep" kalẹ̀ pẹ̀lú àjọṣepọ̀ Phoniks.[2][3] 'Awon' ti kọrin pẹ̀lú ọ̀pọ̀lọpọ̀ àwọn olórin hip hop ilẹ̀ ̀Amẹ́ríkà bíi: Little Brother, Common, EPMD, MC Lyte, ati Oddisee. 
