Nestlé S.A. (pípè ní Faransé: [nɛsle]; English: /ˈnɛsleɪ, ˈnɛsəl, ˈnɛsli/, tì a mó télè si: /ˈnɛsəlz/) jẹ́ ilé-iṣẹ̀ aṣońjẹ ti orílè-èdè Swiss, tí olú-iléesé wọn wà ní Vevey, Vaud, Switzerland. 
Ó jẹ́ ilé-iṣẹ́ asońje tí ó tóbi jùlo ní àgbáyé bí a bá fi òṣùwòn owó pípa wolé àti awon òṣùẁòn mìíràn láti ọdún 2014.[3][4][5][6][7] [9] 
Ògbómọ̀sọ́ jẹ́ ìlú ní ìpínlẹ̀ Ọ̀yo ní apá ìwò-oòrùn oriĺè-èdè Nàìjíríaì. 
A dá ìlú Ògbómọ̀sọ́ sílẹ̀ ní 17th Century.[2] Àpapọ̀ iye àwọn ènìyàn tí ó wà níbè gẹ́gẹ́ ètò ìkànìyàn ọdún 2006 sọ jẹ́ 645,000.[3] Yorùbá pó́ńbélé ni ọ̀pọ̀ àwọn òlùgbé Ògbómọ̀sọ́. 
Iṣẹ́ àgbẹ́ iṣu, gbágùúdá, àgbàdo àti ewé sìgá jẹ́ lára àwọn iṣẹ́ tó gbajúmọ̀ jùlo ni Ògbómọ̀sọ́.[4] 
