Ó jẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ tí ìtumọ̀ rẹ̀ kò dá geere. 
Àbùdá kan gbòógì tí ọ̀rọ̀ tàbí gbólóhùn Pọ́nna máa ń ní ni àìnítumọ̀ kan pàtó. Ó jẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ tàbí gbólóhùn tí ìtumọ̀ rẹ̀ kò dúró sójú kan. Bí àpeere, "Ẹ̀wà"; èyí lè túnmọ sí ohun tí ó dára, bákan náà, ó tún túnmọ sí ẹ̀wà (beans) tí a máa ń jẹ. 
Èyí tó jásí wípé Ṣadé lẹ́wà (Sade is Beautiful) yàtọ̀ sí Ṣadé lẹ́wà (Sade has Beans) 
