Bimbo Oshin jẹ́ òní fíìmù ti orílè-èdè Nàìjíríà . [1] 
Ìgbésí ayé ìbẹ̀rẹ̀ àti iṣẹ́ 
Filmography tí a yàn 
Ní ọdún 2016, wón bu ọlá fun pẹ̀lú Ààmi Ẹka Ẹ̀bùn ní 2016 Afro-Heritage Broadcasting and Entertainment and Awards. [1] 
A bi Hadera ni ojo kini osu kankanla ni ilu Harlem.[1] Oje omo ilu Ethiopia ati Europea lapapo.[2] Baba e Asfaha je asasala Ethiopia Tigrayan ati oludasili African Services Committee, NGO ti o wa ni ilu Harlem eyi ti o man shey iranlowo fun awon oni irin ajo to wa lati Africa[3]. Iya re Kim Nichols je oludari ASC, ohun ati Hadera man yonda arowan le pelu orisirisi eniyan ki oto bere ise osere .[4][5] Hadera se ise olounje fun odun mewa ki oto bere ere sise.[6] 
O lọ si The Harlem School of the Arts, atẹle nipasẹ Fiorello H. LaGuardia High School. 
Hadera lọ siwaju lati gba MFA ni Awọn ẹkọ ọrọ ati Iṣe lati RADA/King's College London.[1] 
Ni odun 2010 Hadera jade ninu fiimu 1/20. Fun igba akoko[1] 
Hadera ṣe alabaṣiṣẹpọ gege bi Stephanie Holden ninu fiimu odun 2017 Baywatch, ati ni ọdun 2018 o ṣe irawọ bi Kay Daniels ninu jara TV Billions. 
O ni o ni a ti nwaye ipa ninu awọn Showtime Series Billions , gebi akọwé fun billionaire Bobby Axelrod, dun nipa Damian Lewis . 
Ilfenesh Hadera (ti a bi ni ojo kini osu kankanla odun 1985) je osere Ethiopian-American . 
O ko pa ninu fiimu Baywatch ti oj jade ni odun 2017 gege bi Stephanie Holden . 
Ni ojo kankandilogbon osu kesan, Hadera bera si ni kopa Mayme Johnson, iyawo Bumpy Johnsonni ifi lole jara titi American , Godfather of Harlem lori Epix.[1] 
Ohun ati Spike Lee ma jon sise ni opolopo igba, oti kopa ninu Da Brick, The Blacklist, Oldboy, Show Me a Hero, Chi-Raq, Chicago Fire, The Punisher ati She's Gotta Have It. 
Awọn ami eye ati awọn yiyan 
Negga ni Cannes Festival odun 2016 
Lori telifisionu Negga ti kopa ninu awon ere Doctors, Criminal Justice ati jara Irish Love Is the Drug. 
O ko pa Doris "Sid" Siddiqi ninu jara BBC Three eyi ti oje Personal Affairs, legbe Laura Aikman, Annabel Scholey ati Maimie McCoy.[1] Negga kopa Rosie ninu awon jara alakoko titi RTÉ's Love/Hate.[2] 
Negga kopa gegebi Dame Shirley Bassey ninu ere TV BBC Shirley ni odun 2011 osi gba ami eye IFTA osere ti odara julo fun ipa. 
Ipa re ninu theartre je Duck ni Titus Andronicus ati Lay Me Down Softly.[1] Ni odun 2007, obere ise pelu Irish theatrical group ni Pan Pan Theatre. 
Ni odun 2010, o ko pa Ophelia ninu ifilole Hamlet lori itage. 
Otun fi ohun re kale fun ere Dark Souls II, okopa Shanalotte, ti atu mosi "Emerald Herald". 
Odun 2013 ni a gba Negga ki o wa kopa Raina ni jara American Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D..[1][2]. Ose afihan ninu ipele metadilogun titi eto na[3] O ko ipa ninu fiimu Steve McQueeneyi ti ogba emi eye Oscar ti akole re je 12 Years a Slave, sugbon won yo ipa re ninu ere na.[4] Ojo kedogbon osu keta odun 2015, Negga ko ipa Tulip O'Hare ninu jara AMC, Preacher, ti o jade ni odun 2016.[5] 
Ni odun 2016, Negga kopa ninu Loving, ti won se ifi lo le eh ni 2016 Cannes Film Festival lehin na ni Toronto International Film Festival.[1][2] Fiimu na da lo ri awon Lovings, toko tiyawo ti won ni awo ara to yato awon odun 1950s ati 1960s ni Virginia, igbe yawo won fju ba ile ejo to ga ju lo, ti esi won deni Loving v. Virginia. 
Negga di ilu moka fun ipa yi,[3] ati pe ogba yiyan ati emi yi lopolopo fun Ami eye Academy fun osere ti odara julo, Ami eye Golden Globe fun ese ori irin eyi ti o dara julo, ati BAFTA Rising Star Award.[4][5] 
Negga kopa ninu ise Gate Theatre’ ti odun 2018 (Yaël Farber lo dari e) ti Hamlet,[1][2] ti otun tunse ni St. Ann’s Warehouse ni orisun 2020.[3][4] 
Negga ati Dominic Cooper n fera wan ni ibere odun 2010. 
Won koko pade ni odun 2009 lori ere ori itage Phèdre pelu Helen Mirren. 
Awon mejeji jo n gbe ni Primrose Hill titi ilu london.[1][2] Won fe ra wan fun odun mefa; sugbon Negga ogba odun die ki awon oniroyin to gbo pe won o fera mo titi di osu kerin odun 2018.[3][4] Negga ti kopa niwaju Cooper ninu fiimu AMC Preacher,ni bi ti won ti kopa ololufe, won si ni ore timotimo ni awon mejeji[4] 
Ruth Negga ( ;[1] ti a bi ni ojo keje osu kini odun 1982)[2] je osere Ethiopian-Irish ti a mo fun ipa re ni jara telifisonu AMC Preacher ati ninu fiimu Loving. . 
Ni odun 2003 won yan Negga gegebi osere tuntun ti o dara julo ni Olivier Awards.[1] Won yan fun irawo ti on goke julo ni odun 2006 ni Berlin Film Festival.[2] Oti gba iyin rere fun ipa re gegebi Mildred Loving ninu fiimu odun 2016 eyi a pe ni Loving, oti gba Academy Award, Critic's Choice, ati Golden Globe Award nominations fun osere ti o dara julo 
