Syndy Emade (ti a bi gege bi Elone Synthia Emade ni ojo kankanlelogun osu kankanla odun 1993) je osere, awose ati agbe ere jade omo ilu Cameroon. 
Oje asoju burandi fun InstaVoice Celeb.[1][2] Ohun ni oda ile ise Blue rain entertainment.[3][4] Awon ere ti oti gbe jade je A Man For The Weekend and Rose on The Grave. 
O jade ninu ere Nigeria Nollywood ni odun 2016 ninu ere "Why I Hate Sunshine"[5] Ni odun 2017, won ko oruko e kale gegebi osere keji ti o sise ju ni ilu Cameroon, awon agbere jade ori ero ayelujara Njoka Tv fun ile Áfríkà[6] Won fun ni ami eye osere obirin ti o dara julo ni ile cameroon, ni ami eye Scoos Academy ni odun 2017.[7] O gba ami eye yeye ini ti Cameroon ni odun 2014.[8] 
Ere ti Emade ko se ni ere "Obsession" ti o jade ni odun 2010[1] ohun ni alaga ati oludasile Blue Rain Entertainment. Ni odun 2017 o gbe ere A Man For The Weekend jade eleyi ti oni osere Nollywood Alexx Ekubo ninu e.[2] 
