Eberechukwu Nwizu [1] tí a tún mọ̀ sí Bhaira Mcwizu tàbí Bayray McNwizu jẹ́ òṣèrébìnrin ọmọ orílẹ̀-èdè Nàìjíríà.[2][3] O dí gbajúmò lẹ́hìn tí ó gbégbá orókè níbi ètò Amstel Malta Box Office (AMBO) ẹlékẹẹ̀ta. 
Ní ọdún 2009, wọ́n yàán fún àmì-ẹ̀yẹ kan ti Africa Movie Academy Awards.[4][5] 
