Aïcha Elhadj Macky (8 Oṣù Kínní Ọdún 1982) jẹ́ olùdarí eré àti olùgbéré-jáde ọmọ orílẹ̀-èdè Nìjẹ̀r. Ó tún jẹ́ onímọ̀ nípa àwùjọ.[1] Ó gbajúmọ̀ jùlọ fún dídarí eré tí àkọ́lé rẹ̀ jẹ́ The Fruitless Tree.[2] 
