Pascale Lamche (tí wọ́n bí ní Oṣù Keèje, Ọdún 1960) jẹ́ olùdarí eré àti olùgbéréjáde ọmọ orílẹ̀-èdèFránsì àti Gúúsù Áfríkà. 
Ó gbajúmọ̀ fún dídarí àwọn eré tí ó lórúkọ bíi Stalingrad, Black Diamond, Pakistan Zindabad, French Beauty, Accused #1: Nelson Mandela, Sophiatown àti Winnie.[1] Ó tún maá n ṣiṣẹ́ gẹ́gẹ́ bíi ònkọ̀tàn àti olùyàwòrán eré.[2] 
