Ìgbésí ayé 
Naa Ashorkor fẹ́ olólùfẹ́ rẹ̀ tipẹ́tipẹ́ Ahuma Cabutey Adodoadji ní ọdún 2014. [1] Ní ọjọ́ karùndínlógún Oṣù Kẹjọ ọdún 2017, ó kéde pé òun bímọ lórí itẹjade iroyin. [2] 
Ó kéde pé òun bímọ ẹlẹ́ẹ̀kejì tí ó tún jẹ́ ọmọkùnrin ni ọjọ kínní Oṣù Keje ọdún 2019. [1] 
Àwọn ìtọ́kasì 
Ó gba àmì ẹ̀yẹ fún òṣèré tí ó dára jùlọ ní ọdún 2010 ní African Movie Academyfún ipa tí ó kó nínú "The Perfect Picture" ní ọdún (2009). [1] [2] Naa Ashorkor tún ṣe eré pẹ̀lú Yvonne Okoro, Joselyn Dumas àti John Dumelo . 
Iṣẹ́ 
Naa Ashorkor, pẹ̀lú òṣèré Chris Attoh olóòtú Vodafone Ghana Music Awards ní ọdún 2016 (VGMAs 2016) [1] tí ó wáyé ní Accra International Conference Centre . Ó tún jẹ́ olóòtú ìdíje Miss Maliaka fún ọdún mẹ́jọ. 
[2] Ní ọdún 2008, ó ṣe ìfarahàn nínú eré tí ó kọ́kọ́ ṣe tí Shirley Frimpong Manso darí. Ó jẹ́ onísòwò ní dìí okòwò méjì: Jaarno, Okòwò ayélujára ti oun jíjẹ àti April Communications, èyí tí ó jẹmọ́ iṣẹ́ eré ìtàgé. [3] Ó jẹ́ agbóhùnsáfẹ́fẹ́ pẹ̀lú Multimedia Group láti ọdún 2017 títí di ọdún 2020 níbití ó ti ṣe olóòtú èto "Showbiz A-Z" àti "Strong and Sassy". [4] Ó lọ sí ilé iṣẹ́ agbóhùnsáfẹ́fẹ́ Asaase ní ìparí Oṣù Kàrún ọdún 2020 tí ó sì ṣe olóòtú "Between Hours" àti "Just Us" . 
