Àwon ilé-isé nla nla ni orilẹ-ede Naijiria bi- Etisalat Nigeria, [1] Airtel Nigeria, [2] Ford Foundation Nigeria [3] ati Olaniwun Ajayi & Co [4] - kalè sí Bana na Island. 
Díè ninú awọn olugbe ibè 
