Civic tower, ti a tun npe ni Civic Center Towers, Civic Towers, jẹ ile-iṣẹ oní pètésì merindinlogun(16)kan [1] [2] ile-iṣẹ ni ìpínlè Eko(awọn miiran sọ pe marundinlogun ni). [3] [4] Kò jinna [5] si Civic Center ni Ozumba Mbadiwe Avenue, Victoria Island, ìpínlè Eko . [6] A si ni ọdun 2015, onisowo Uzor Christopher si ni ó nií[7] 
