Idibo fun ipo Gomina ipinle Eko waye ni ojo kokanla osu kerin odun 2015. 
Oludije ẹgbẹ oṣelu All Progressives Congress (APC) Akinwunmi Ambode, ti o jẹ oniṣiro agba fun ipinlẹ Eko tẹlẹ, bori oludije ẹgbẹ oṣelu People’s Democratic Party (PDP) Jimi Agbaje ati oludije Alliance for Democracy (AD) Bolaji Ogunseye. 
Gomina ati igbakeji gomina ni a yan lori tikẹti kanna. [1] 
Ogbeni Jimi Agbaje ni o jawe olubori ti o de fi si ipo lati se asoju egbe PDP ninu idibo gomina ipinle eko. PDP primary results[3] Party Candidate Votes % PDP Jimi Agbaje 434 50 PDP Musiliu Obanikoro 346 39.86 PDP Tokunbo Kamson 46 5.29 PDP Deji Doherty 21 2.41 PDP Babatunde Gbadamosi 21 2.41 Total votes 868 100 
