Oluchi Mercy Okorie tí a bí ní ọjọ́ kejìdínlọgbọ̀n osù kẹjọ ọdún 1981 ní Ìlú Èkó jẹ́ agbábọ́ọ̀lù sínú agbọ̀n ti orílẹ̀-ède Nàìjíríà tẹ́lẹ̀ rí tí ó gbábọ́ọ̀lù fún First Bank BC àti ẹgbẹ́ orílẹ̀-ède Nàìjíríà . 
Ó ṣe aṣojú Nàìjíríà ní bi 2005, 2006 àti 2007 FIBA Africa Championship . [1] [2] 
iṣẹ́ Ìdárayá síse 
Láti ogúnjọ́ sí ọjọ́ kejìdínlọ́gbọ̀n Oṣù kejìlá, ní gbọ̀ngàn eré ìdárayá inú ilé ní Abuja, Nàìjíríà tí wọ́n ti gbàlejò FIBA Africa Championship fún àwọn obìnrin ní ọdún 2005 . 
Níbi ayeye náà, Oluchi ló sojú orílẹ̀-ède Nàìjíríà tó sì gba ààmì ẹ̀yẹ wúrà. [1] 
Ní bi 2006 FIBA Africa Women's Club Champions Cup èyí tí ó kópa, Oluchi gba ààmì ẹ̀yẹ idẹ. 
