O jú àmì mẹwa fún eré kọ̀ọ̀kan ní Tokyo, ní ọdún 2020 [1] Akẹkọọ̀ jade akọ̀kọ̀ ní ilé ìwé gíga Arizona State University tí ó jẹ́ agbá bọ́ọ̀lù inú agbọ̀n obìnrin tí ó kájú láti ṣe ẹgbẹ́ Olympic [2] Ọmọ ẹgbẹ́ 2019 FIBA African Championship Gold Medal tí ó kópa nínu Ìdíje ayẹyẹ Pre-Olympic [2] agbá bọ́ọ̀lù inú agbọ̀n Arizona ti ọdún 2011 [2] Ẹni tí ó yára jùlọ nínú ọgọrún mita àti igba mita gẹ́gẹ́ bí ẹni tí ó sẹ̀sẹ̀ wọ ilé-ìwé gíga [2] 
