Olukorede S. Yishau jẹ́ òǹkọ̀wé àti akọ̀ròyìn ọmọ orílẹ̀èdè Nàìjíríà . 
Ó ti ṣe atokọ pípẹ́ fún ẹ̀bùn 2021 Nà̀ij̀iríà fún Litiréṣọ̀ . [1] [2] [3] 
Ìbẹ̀rẹ̀ pẹ̀pẹ̀ ayé re àti iṣẹ́ 
A bí Yishau ni Ṣomolu, ní ̀ipínlẹ̀ Èkó . 
Ó kẹ́kọ̀ọ́ nípa ìbánisọ̀rọ̀ púpọ̀ ní Ambrose Alli University, Ekpoma . [1] Ó ti ṣiṣẹ́ bí oníṣẹ́ ìròyìn ní Orísun, Sọ Ìwé ìròhìn àti pé ó jẹ́ Olóòtú Alábàáṣepọ̀ lọ́wọ́lọ́wọ́ ní Ìwé ìròhìn Nation . [2] [3] [4] 
Ìwé àkosílẹ̀ 
Àwọn ìtọ́kasí 
Ile-ẹkọ giga Summit, Offa jẹ ile-ẹkọ giga ti aladani ti a da ni ọdun 2015 ati pe o wa ni Offa . [1] Ile-ẹkọ giga jẹ ohun ini ati ti iṣeto nipasẹ awujo Ansar-Ud-Deen ti Nigeria , ẹgbẹ Musulumi ti a ṣeto fun idi idagbasoke ẹkọ ti awọn Musulumi ati awujọ Musulumi ni Nigeria. [2] a da Ile-ẹkọ naa papọ pẹlu awọn ile-ẹkọ giga aladani mẹsan miiran ni Nigeria ni ọdun 2015. 
Apa Omowe 
Ile-ẹkọ naa bẹrẹ iṣẹ ni kikun ni Oṣu kọkanla, ọdun 2016 pẹlu awọn ọmọ ile-iwe ẹ̀ẹ́dẹ́gbẹ́ta (500), awọn iṣẹ ikẹkọ ti o wa lati ṣe ni ile-ẹknaa ọ pẹlu: [1] [2] 
Isedale (biology) Chemistry (chemistry) Fisiksi (physics) Iṣiro Imo komputa science Awọn ẹkọ Larubawa Awọn ẹkọ Islam Eko ede geesi ati literary studies Oro aje Awọn ẹkọ Iṣowo Imọ Oselu Iṣiro (Accounting) 
Igbakeji olori ile eko giga 
Igbakeji olori ile eko giga ti o je oludasile ti Summit University, Offa ni Ojogbon Hussein Oloyede. [1] Igbakeji Alakoso ti fi da gbogbo eniyan loju wipe ile-ẹkọ naa yoo jẹ ọkan ninu ile-ẹkọ giga aladani ti o din owo julọ ni Nigeria. 
Igbakeji olori ile eko giga pẹlu awọn Igbakeji olori ile eko giga ti awọn ile eko aladani miiran ti bẹ Ijọba ipinle nigeria lati gba awọn ile-ẹkọ giga aladani laaye ki won je ni anfani lati awọn iṣẹ akanṣe TETFUnd (Tertiary Education Trust Fund), lati jẹ kye ki wọn tẹsiwaju lati pese eto-ẹkọ didara si gbogbo eniyan. [2] 
Ngozi Alaegbu jẹ́ akọròyìn àti olóòtú ètò orí ẹ̀rọ-amóhùnmáwòrán.[1] Ó ti ṣiṣẹ́ ní Degue Broadcasting Network (DBN), Television Continental (TVC). Lọ́wọ́lọ́wọ́, ó sì ń ṣịṣẹ́ pẹ̀lú Arise TV.[2] 
Ìgbésíayé rẹ̀ 
Alaegbu kẹ́kọ̀ọ́ gboyè nínú ẹ̀kọ́ German ní University of Hamburg, Germany.[1] Ó bẹ̀rẹ̀ iṣẹ́ rẹ̀ nípasẹ̀ ṣíṣẹ iṣẹ́ pẹ̀lú DBN. 
Lẹ́yìn náà, ó lọ sí TVC, níbi tí ó ti lo àwọn ọdún díẹ̀ ṣáájú kí ó tó fi ipò náà sílẹ̀ ní oṣù kẹjọ, ọdún 2019.[2] Ìṣípòpadà Alaegbu sí Arise TV ṣẹlẹ̀ ní oṣụ̀ kejì, ọdún 2020.[3] 
Àwọn àmì-ẹ̀yẹ rẹ̀ 
Alaegbu gba àmì-ẹ̀yẹ ti akaròyìn tó dára jù lọ lórí ẹ̀rọ̀ amóhu ̀nmáwòrán ní ọdún 2021, èyí tó jẹ́ ti Nigeria Media Merit Awards.[1] Wọ́n to orúkọ rẹ̀ sí ipò karùndínlógún lára àwọn obìnrin alágbára jù lọ nínú iṣẹ́ akọ̀ròyìn, láti ọ̀wọ́ àwọn Women in Journalism, ní ọdún 2021.[2] 
Ìgbésí ayé ara ẹni 
Alaegbu jẹ́ ìyà àti ìyá-ìyá, ìyẹn ni pé àwọn ọmọ rẹ̀ ti ń bímọ, ó sì ti ní àwọn ọmọ-ọmọ.[1] 
