Donisia Daniel Minja tí a bí ní ọjọ́ kẹsán Oṣù Kẹjọ ọdún 1999 jẹ́ ogbóǹtarìgì agbábọ́ọ̀lù ọmọ orílẹ̀-ède Tanzania tí ó ṣeré ipò iwájú lórí pápá fún Yanga Princess àti ẹgbẹ́ agbábọ́ọ̀lù obìnrin Tanzania . [1] 
Isẹ́ òkè-òkun 
Ní ọdún 2018, Minja mi àwọ̀n pẹ̀lú àmì ayò mẹ́ta ní bi ìdíje CECAFA Women’s Championship ti ọdún 2018 láti gba àmì ẹ̀yẹ ẹni tí ó mi àwọ̀n jùlọ ní bi ìdíje náà. [1] [2] [3] 
